353,IssuesEvent,2015-04-18 16:39:51+00:00,8600174,Lagg/steamodd,423776,ondrowan,,,opened,vdf.dump doesn't seem to work with io module,[],[],0,"I was trying to figure out some example for `dumps` I'd use in VDF documentation when I noticed it works well with built-in `open`, but fails with `io` module.

