3169,IssuesEvent,2017-12-11 16:01:29+00:00,74750706,adamcharnock/django-adminlte2,1908663,gbts,,,opened,Header template crashes in Django 2.x,[],[],0,"Since `User.is_authenticated` is now a property in Django 2.x, the `is_authenticated()` call in `templatetags/adminlte_helpers.py` now raises an exception. There's PR #11 that removes the parentheses but it would break compatibility with <2.x, so something like

    user = context['request'].user if user is None else user
    authenticated = user.is_authenticated
    authenticated = authenticated() if callable(authenticated) else authenticated
    return 'https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/{hash}?s={size}&d=mm'.format(
