WARNING: the astropy_helpers.extern.automodapi.autodoc_enhancements extension does not declare if it is safe for parallel reading, assuming it isn't - please ask the extension author to check and make it explicit
```

We should figure out if ``autodoc_enhancements`` is indeed safe for parallel reading, and if so, do what needs to be done so we enable it.",{},{}
