5115,IssuesEvent,2018-02-28 00:45:34+00:00,3470471,FortAwesome/Font-Awesome,2529208,nwpappas,1505683,FortAwesome,opened,Q: How to build custom SVG/JS library?,[],[],0,"I am trying to build a smaller [SVG/JS library](https://fontawesome.com/how-to-use/svg-with-js) using FA5's npm packages. I can build the library, but am unsure how to automatically parse when the library is imported.

