```javascript
import fontawesome from '@fortawesome/fontawesome';
import fasCoffee from '@fortawesome/fontawesome-free-solid/faCoffee';

fontawesome.library.add(fasCoffee);

export default fontawesome;
```

The package builds, but when I include it in my HTML the icons are not automatically parsed. I have to go to the console and type:

```javascript
MyFA5.dom.i2svg()
```

How do cause my bundle to automatically parse the icons when it is included in an HTML `script` tag?",{},{}
