I tried to create a user with username `иван` (ivan in cyrillic) but was not able to.


### Expected behavior

Create a new user  OR  show validation error.


### User-facing consequences

Cannot create usernames in other locales.


### Errors and logs

UI doesn't show a validation error, but JS console has this:

<img width=""880"" alt=""screen shot 2018-08-30 at 5 01 06 pm"" src=""https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/163966/44857106-c4f0c800-ac77-11e8-8976-bfbf9f6924fd.png"">


### Steps to reproduce

  - Go to localhost:8080/facility/#/users
  - Choose ADD USER
  - Enter a non-ascii username (and valid password etc)
  - Click ADD

Actual: nothing

