5999,IssuesEvent,2016-09-26 19:55:10+00:00,14991049,nccgroup/Scout2,914105,jutulen,4067082,nccgroup,opened,Feature request: History ,[],[],0,"Would it be possible to add some history functionality to the tool? The way it currently works is that the JSON file with the results are overwritten each time the script is run. 

