9209,IssuesEvent,2018-08-20 16:31:33+00:00,71482397,Parsl/parsl,29691029,ConnorPigg,26490185,Parsl,opened,Change Local Database Strategy from Many Writers to a Single Writer,"[{'id': 465598056, 'node_id': 'MDU6TGFiZWw0NjU1OTgwNTY=', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/Parsl/parsl/labels/enhancement', 'name': 'enhancement', 'color': '84b6eb', 'default': True}]","[{'login': 'ConnorPigg', 'id': 29691029, 'node_id': 'MDQ6VXNlcjI5NjkxMDI5', 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/29691029?v=4', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ConnorPigg', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/ConnorPigg', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ConnorPigg/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ConnorPigg/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ConnorPigg/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ConnorPigg/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ConnorPigg/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ConnorPigg/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ConnorPigg/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ConnorPigg/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/ConnorPigg/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",0,"Currently, local database logging follows the same pattern as Elasticsearch logging in that each worker connects directly to log storage to write their own resource usage. This causes issues with the SQLite database that only handles single writers. The proposal is to change the workers to send information back to the machine that started the Parsl run and have that be the sole writer of both resource and status updates to the database. This will ideally solve the inconsistencies with local database logging and be more in line with what other successful projects that include task monitoring do.",{},{}
